        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="导读"><a href="#导读" class="headerlink" title="导读"></a>导读</h1><p>前些日子在捣鼓dplayer，但是没能成功，可还是想要把视频嵌入到博客上，可是b站本身的嵌入模式太恶心了，看了很多文章，得到了这种方法。</p><h1 id="教程"><a href="#教程" class="headerlink" title="教程"></a>教程</h1><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">style</span>=<span class="string">&quot;position: relative; width: 100%; height: 0; padding-bottom: 75%;&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">iframe</span> <span class="attr">XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX</span> <span class="attr">scrolling</span>=<span class="string">&quot;no&quot;</span> <span class="attr">border</span>=<span class="string">&quot;0&quot;</span> <span class="attr">frameborder</span>=<span class="string">&quot;no&quot;</span> <span class="attr">framespacing</span>=<span class="string">&quot;0&quot;</span> <span class="attr">allowfullscreen</span>=<span class="string">&quot;true&quot;</span> <span class="attr">style</span>=<span class="string">&quot;position: absolute; width: 100%; height: 100%; Left: 0; top: 0;&quot;</span> &gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">iframe</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在一个正常的视频上点击嵌入代码。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Sinhoole/sincoscot/img/202308111359130.png"></p><p>将代码中的XXX替换为高亮内容。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Sinhoole/sincoscot/img/202308111401278.png"><br>接下来复制这串代码，你就能体会到比较好的播放体验。</p><div style="position: relative; width: 100%; height: 0; padding-bottom: 75%;"><iframe src="//player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid=955927689&bvid=BV1dW4y1o7dp&cid=1196863278&page=1" scrolling="no" border="0" frameborder="no" framespacing="0" allowfullscreen="true" style="position: absolute; width: 100%; height: 100%; Left: 0; top: 0;" ></iframe></div><p><code>Good show for you.</code></p>]]></content>
      
      
